{"id":189822,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-20111018/","date":"2011-10-19T04:30:57Z","modified":"2011-10-19T04:38:34Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 2011/10/18","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/qqXbbc\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">四川阿坝县城附近，再有一位尼姑自焚</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；一天前，阿坝当地藏人示威游行，警察开枪，伤两人。</span></span><span><span>Tibetan nun burns herself to death to protest Chinese rule </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/oct/17/china-tibetan-resistance-self-immolation\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在为西藏人的抗</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拒</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">火上浇油</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——西藏年轻人一连串的自焚抗议，向中国发出警告：先发制人的压制措施可能会引发绝望行为。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalspin.blogs.time.com/2011/10/17/in-beijing-the-party-and-the-police-all-have-a-say-on-culture/#ixzz1b5uLFYqq\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在北京，党内精英和警察都可以对文化说三道四</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共中央全会为文化制定的目标和措施可能过于笼统，但是警察对于文化的干预可是很切实的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社分析：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20111017/wl_nm/us_china_taiwan_election\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国紧张地关注着台湾的选举</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——大陆倾向于国民党继续执政，保持两岸关系进一步发展，同时批评反对党将恶化两岸交往。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20111017/ap_on_re_as/as_china_politics\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的权力交接凸显军队的角色</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中央政治局里军人占</span></span><span><span>18%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，是不容忽视的力量。其中有些将军嗓门尤其大，比如属于太子党的刘源。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20111018/ap_on_re_as/as_china_politics\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共领导人号召发起文化攻势</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国中央全会发表公告，强调文化作为国家软实力和竞争力的重要部分。同时他们在闭门安排未来的人事交接。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/Chinas-Communist-Party-plans-cultural-change-second-time-in-history/articleshow/10404130.cms\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共计划开始</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">其</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">历史上</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">第二次文化改革</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中共对于宣传的酷爱在中央全会的公告中显露无遗，提出了新的文化指导政策。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/10/chinas-bystander-effect.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：中国的旁观者效应</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——幼童被车碾压而无人救助的事情，尽管骇人听闻，但它所反映出来的同情心、道德和法律问题对于中国人来说却不陌生</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/10/18/opinion/kreuger-china-incident/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国幼童被撞事件，暴露了助人为乐的困境</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——看到这起惨剧的录像，很容易去指责当地的文化出了问题，但问题并不这么简单。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/10/18/real-name-system-proposed-for-chinas-rowdy-microbloggers/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国火爆的微博可能会实行实名制</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——关于政府将加强对微博管控的传言一直都有，但最近这似乎要到摊牌的时候了。《北京日报》发文称微博应该实名制</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/18/two-more-arguments-im-tired-of-hearing/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于中国的另外两个老生常谈（续昨）</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国是个大国，人口太多”和“西方总想阻止中国的崛起”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海人博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://shanghaiist.com/2011/10/18/photos_huaxis_50th_anniversary_-_gl.php?gallery0Pic=27#photo-25\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】华西村猎奇</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——关于华西村的雷人图片，只有更多，没有最多。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20111018/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_credit_crunch\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国温州的债务恐慌可能会引发更大担忧</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——温州的私企商人可能正处于中国式次贷危机的核心，但中国的债务危险绝不仅限于温州</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/oh0yCA\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在猪肉门事件中，重庆关闭了沃尔玛的全部</span>13<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">家门店</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；其中国区总裁陈耀昌离职，亚洲总裁斯科特临时接管。</span></span><span><span>Wal-Mart Asia Chief Takes Over China Stores Amid Pork Probe </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/helenwang/2011/10/13/beware-of-crocodile-entering-the-ocean/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">小心鳄鱼入大海</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——关于马云要买雅虎的传闻甚嚣尘上。但马云当年并没有能让雅虎中国起死回生，他如何指望别人相信他能让雅虎美国活过来呢？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/china-vs-the-us-the-case-for-second-place-10132011.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对美国：谁来当老二</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国不久就会超过美国成为世界最大经济体。但作者认为美国在其他生活质量方面的水平仍高于中国，因而对此不必太在意</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/2011/10/18/promoting-effective-china-u-s-strategic-nuclear-dialogue/5zrr\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">促进</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">有效的中美战略核对话</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——本分分析了中国核武器部门的背景和历史，指出美国应大力在中国二炮部队中培养技术专家，通过专家来促进双方交流的效率。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》两年前，奥巴马总统在哥本哈根气候峰会上高调出场；两年过去了，几乎所有的国家认为气候变化是一个严重的问题，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nyti.ms/ojY2nW\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">而美国政坛对此已经失去了兴趣，停留在空谈</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/10/17/world/europe/russia-putin-interview/index.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在普京宣布参选总统的第一个电视专访中，他说他的目标是稳固和多元化俄罗斯经济</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，同时加强国家的政治体系和民主制度的基石。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/18/opinion/18iht-edpantucci18.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">俄国的东方焦虑</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——普京访华虽然表面热闹，但俄国实际上对中国在前苏联各共和国的影响感到不安。普京提出的欧亚联盟就是旨在抗衡这种影响</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/rjTg22\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">五角大楼周一否认有关美伊无法就</span>2011<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年底之后部分美军驻伊问题达成协议的报道</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，称谈判仍在进行中。</span></span><span><span>Pentagon: Troop talks with Iraq &#39;ongoing&#39; </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/indiarealtime/2011/10/18/india-raises-its-game-in-burma/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度在缅甸向中国叫板</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中印两个大国的博弈，在资源丰富的缅甸愈演愈烈。印度在努力加大对缅甸的投资，力争把缅甸拉拢过来。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">詹姆斯敦基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38523&#038;cHash=12414c2fc3d7bb7d7d02b379b681387a\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京努力对付金融领域的潜在危机</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——初夏以来，中国数以千记的中小企业破产，中央政府对于地下金融市场问题反应迟钝，加剧了问题的严重性。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.wsj.com/prIwRH\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国第三季度</span>GDP<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">增速放慢为</span>9.1%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，但仍属健康</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，似乎说明中国经济正在软着陆。北京是否将很快放松经济政策，专家们观点不一。</span></span><span><span>China&#39;s Economic Growth Slows </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》社论：我们不喜欢中国蓄意压低货币，让出口更便宜的政策；</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/nBVgUw\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">但是把美国糟糕的经济表现归因于中国的货币政策，这让我们忽视了更本质的问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：美国政治领袖无法在短期内重振经济，在长期无法达成预算平衡。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：美商会主席：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.wsj.com/pmEGAK\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">如果美国国会通过针对中国如何管理自己货币的法案，中国将进行报复</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>Chamber of Commerce CEO: China Currency Bill Invites Retaliation </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>ChinaHush</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahush.com/2011/10/18/school-labels-underachieving-students-with-green-scarf/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+ChinaHush+%28ChinaHush%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国学校让成绩不好的孩子带绿领巾</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——孔子提倡的“有教无类”的思想，在西安的这座小学里绝无藏身之地。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《归途列车》</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.pbs.org/pov/lasttrainhome/photo_gallery_documentaries-china-recommendations.php#.Tp0wuH5Fqfc.twitter\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">导演范立新和其他电影人推荐关于中国或由中国制作人的纪录片</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>Essential Documentaries About China </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/oTPPQw\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国统计局公布住房价格监控结果</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>16</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">座城市价格下降，</span></span><span><span>24</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">座城市仍在上升。</span></span><span><span>Home Prices Rise in Fewer Than Half of Chinese Cities on Curbs </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/oct/15/chinese-restaurant-dog-meat-myth\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“约克郡的中餐馆里有狗肉卖！”：为什么这类奇闻会被传开？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——华裔作家张丽佳撰文，称对于中国的“奇怪”食物的热衷，其实也是种族主义。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；到iTunes 中搜索“译者”即可订阅和下载译者播客Podcast；点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/p/download.html\">这里</a>可以播放和下载所有译者已公开的视频、音频和杂志。（下载需翻墙）。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-7468242718993351863?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}